divs: Sighting DetailsI was playing in the rain with my big brother and our female friend. We weretrying to clog the sewer and make the water not got in. Then there was a flashof lightning and my borther said look at the sky. I did there were pink-rosecolor lights in a triangular form. Another flash of lightning occured. They weregone. They believe it was a plane. They will denie it but they were there andsaw it. I believe anything is possible.
